verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Mine eyes have seen the glory of the coming of
The Lord;
He is trampling out the vintage where the grapes
Of wrath are stored;
He hath loosed the fateful lightning of His
Terrible swift sword;
His truth is marching on.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I have seen Him in the watchfires of a hundred circling camps;
They have builded Him an altar in the evening
Dews and damps;
I can read His righteous sentence by the dim and
Flaring lamps,
His day is marching on.{/lang-eng}
